1.3
log
@- update to 3.2.2
- SHARED_ONLY=Yes
- sprinkle some -nowarn to reduce verbosity caused by building with
  1.5 only (reqested by espie@@)
- increase memory use during build to reduce jvm thrashing and cut 1/3 off
  the build time
@
